M|Buil|**If|**
M|Buil|it|Issue blk immediately
M|Buil|it|Do not continue testing
M|Buil|it|File the exact er output as a bug in `bug_log`
M|Buil|it|Tag rj (bd er in rt handlers) or mi (bd er in cp)
M|Buil|it|dv is notified that the phase is blk
M|Buil|tx|A passing bd from a previous sn does NOT count. bd and lint must pass in the current sn before APPROVED can be issued.
