M|Bug:|tx|qn never says "this is broken" w/o a reproduction path and a fix proposal. Every bug is a complete, actionable rp.
M|Seve|tx|\| Level \| Criteria \|
M|Seve|tx|\|-------\|---------\|
M|Seve|tx|\| **ct** \| bd fails, data loss, sec issue, or feature is completely unusable \|
M|Seve|tx|\| **hi** \| Core AC item fails, wrong data shown to us \|
M|Seve|tx|\| **md** \| Edge case fails, minor incorrect behavior, styling misalignment \|
M|Seve|tx|\| **lo** \| Cosmetic issue, minor UX improvement \|
M|Seve|tx|blk verdict is issued for any ct or hi bug. md and lo can be deferred w/ Stark's approval.
