M|QA R|tx|```markdown
M|QA R|**Ve|APPROVED / blk**
M|Buil|- `n|✅ Zero er / ❌ [er count]
M|Buil|- `n|✅ Zero warnings / ❌ [wn count]
M|Acce|tx|\| # \| Criteria \| Result \| Notes \|
M|Acce|tx|\|---\|---------\|--------\|-------\|
